            </p>

            <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="confirmation-button" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #f97316; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; text-align: center;">
                Confirm Account
