                If that doesn't work, copy and paste the following link in your browser:
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #f97316; font-weight: 600; word-break: break-all; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                <a href="{{verificationLink}}" style="color: #f97316; text-decoration: underline;">{{verificationLink}}</a>
            </p>

            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.625; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                If you have any questions, just reply to this email&mdash;we're always happy to help out.
            </p>

            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">
                Cheers,
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">
                The Arena Team
            </p>
        </div>

